Biography

William Joseph Cronin (1913-1998)

William Cronin was born in Queensland, Australia

Birth

William Joseph Cronin was born 15 May 1913 at Queensland, Australia. He was the son of James Cronin and Maria Moore. [1]

Marriage

William Joseph Cronin married Lillian Ruby Pilcher 09 March 1943 at Queensland, Australia. [2]

Residence & Occupation

The Australian Electoral Roll for 1943 records: William Joseph Cronin, occupation: Police Constable and his wife, Lillian Ruby Cronin, occupation: Home Duties, are living at the Police Station, Blair Athol, Queensland, Australia.

The Australian Electoral Roll for 1954 records: William Joseph Cronin, occupation: Police Sergeant and his wife, Lillian Ruby Cronin, occupation: Home Duties, are living at Henry Street, Nanango, Queensland, Australia.

The Australian Electoral Roll for 1963 records: William Joseph Cronin, occupation: Police Sergeant and his wife, Lillian Ruby Cronin, occupation: Home Duties, are living at 35A Curtis Street, Bundaberg, Queensland, Australia.

The Australian Electoral Roll for 1977 records: William Joseph Cronin, occupation: Farmer and his wife, Lillian Ruby Cronin, occupation: Home Duties, and James Joseph Cronin, occupation: Teacher, are living at 9 Pottinger Street, Toowoomba, Queensland, Australia.

The Australian Electoral Roll for 1980 records: William Joseph Cronin, occupation: Farmer, and his wife, Lillian Ruby Cronin, occupation: Home Duties, are living at 9 Pottinger Street, Toowoomba, Queensland, Australia. [3]

Death

William Joseph Cronin passed age 86, away 23 July 1999 at St Andrew's Hospital, Toowoomba, Queensland, Australia. [4]

Burial

William Joseph Cronin was buried on 27 July 1999 at Cabarlah Cemetery, Cabarlah, Queensland, Australia. He shares the grave with his wife, Lilian Ruby (Pilcher) Cronin. [5]

Research Note

CARE There are 2 males named William Joseph Cronin, both born in 1913. They are not the same person.

William Joseph Cronin (21 August 1913-14 May 1993) was the son of Michael Cronin & Bridget (Murphy) Cronin.

William Joseph Cronin (15 May 1913-23 July 1999) was the son of James Cronin & Maria (Moore) Cronin.

Please do not confuse them Diane Darcy
